# The rendered, self-contained notebook (embedded figures) IS committed as the
# scrollable deliverable, alongside the Typst PDF. The .qmd is the Quarto source
# of truth.

# Derived-result cache (.cache/) pickles
*.pkl

# NLR API credentials (see .env.example). Never commit a populated .env.
.env

# uv-managed environment
.venv/

# Quarto caches and intermediates. The trailing * matters: a render that is
# interrupted (or run while another is in flight) leaves numbered siblings like
# `*.quarto_ipynb_17`, which a bare `*.quarto_ipynb` pattern does not match.
.quarto/
*_files/
*.quarto_ipynb*

# Rendered document HTML is a dev/preview artifact (the .ipynb and .pdf are the
# committed deliverables). Scoped to the repo root so figures/*.html is unaffected.
/*.html

__pycache__/
.DS_Store
.ipynb_checkpoints/
